videos.description: Daniel Oturu throws down a dunk in the middle of two defenders as Minnesota leads early vs. Michigan.
videos.headline: Oturu throws down two-handed slam

videos.description: Jon Teske drains a long 3-pointer as the Wolverines tie the game with the Golden Gophers late in the first half.
videos.headline: Teske drains 3 to tie Golden Gophers

videos.description: Ignas Brazdeikis puts up a huge and-1 as Michigan keeps it close with Minnesota.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis puts up big and-1

videos.description: Isaiah Livers puts up a big dunk that gets the hometown Michigan crowd riled up in the second half.
videos.headline: Livers throws dunk down to get home crowd hyped
